featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Eid Gah Nichlaul. This Idgah is towards the north near Nichlaul police station. "Eidul Fitr" and "Eidul Azha" prayers are offered every year in this Eidgah. Eidul Fitr and Eidul Azha prayers are offered every year from 6:30am to 9:00am. Which is taught by Imam Sahib (Maulana Sahib) of Darul Oloom Nichlaul Madrasa. After offering Namaz, people go to their homes in silence.
